### auth.http

### 1. 회원가입 (기존 user가 있으면 스킵)
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "테스트",
  "nickname": "테스터",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!@"
}

### 2. 로그인 성공
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!@"
}

### 3. 로그인 실패 - 잘못된 비밀번호
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "WrongPassword123!"
}

### 4. 로그인 실패 - 존재하지 않는 이메일
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "notexist@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!@"
}

### 5. Validation 실패 - 이메일 형식 오류
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "Test1234!@"
}